title: Box Brown - Bellen!, Chubby Chasers, Fuck Shits
description:
All of these three books are available at Box Brown's website on a "Pay What You Want" basis, so if you'd rather put a few bucks (or a few cents) in the creators pocket you can go there to grab them.

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

'Dizzying Highs and Staggering Lows - The Complete Bellen! Comics 2006-2010' collects Box Brown's 'Bellen!'web comic in it's entirety. 689 pages

'Chubby Chasers' is an out-of-print mini-comic from 2012 that includes additional color pages. 30 pages

'Fuck Shits' is a 32-page out-of-print mini-comic contains two stories: Best Friends Forever (in full color) and Blast-Off. Two comics about teenagers doing teenager stuff. 36 pages
